'''苏安励'''（{{lang-en|Arne Morris Sorenson}}， {{bd|1958年|10月13日|2021年|2月15日|catIdx=Sorenson}}）是一位美国企业家，中文名叫'''苏安励'''。

== 生平 ==
1958年出生于[[日本|日本]][[东京都|东京都]]，<ref>{{Cite web|last=Jenkins|first=Courtney|date=June 7, 2017|title=Q&A with Arne Sorenson: Architect of Change|url=https://www.hoteliermagazine.com/qa-arne-sorenson-architect-change/|access-date=October 11, 2019|website=Hotelier Magazine|language=en-US}}</ref><ref name=":3" /><ref>{{cite book|url = https://books.google.ca/books?id=X2LaAAAAMAAJ&q=Arne+Morris+Sorenson+Morris+Dorothy&dq=Arne+Morris+Sorenson+Morris+Dorothy&hl=en&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwj0-7P1wfDuAhVEAp0JHa12B4YQ6AEwBXoECAUQAQ|title=  Who's who in Religion|page = 366|year = 1985|publisher = Marquis Who's Who}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url = https://honsafamilyfuneral.com/book-of-memories/2764317/sorenson-dorothy/obituary.php|title = Obituary for Dorothy Austin Sorenson|website = Honsa Family Funeral Home}}</ref>1965年回到[[美国|美国]]，1983年毕业于[[明尼苏达大学法学院|明尼苏达大学法学院]]。<ref name=":2">{{Cite news|last=Hagerty|first=Craig Karmin and James R.|date=February 16, 2021|title=Marriott CEO Arne Sorenson Dies at Age 62|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/marriott-international-says-president-ceo-arne-sorenson-died-11613483225|access-date=February 17, 2021|issn=0099-9660}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Lebowitz Rossi|first1=Holly|date=November 11, 2014|title=7 CEOs with notably devout religious beliefs|url=http://fortune.com/2014/11/11/7-ceos-with-notably-devout-religious-beliefs/|access-date=June 27, 2016|website=Fortune|publisher=Time}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=December 15, 2011|title=Arne Sorenson ('83) Named New Marriott CEO|publisher=[[University_of_Minnesota|University of Minnesota]]|url=http://www.law.umn.edu/news/arne-sorenson-named-new-marriott-ceo-12-15-2011.html}}</ref>之后进入[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|华盛顿哥伦比亚特区]]一家律师事务所，之后成为合伙人，负责[[併購|併購]]业务。<ref name=":1">{{Cite news|date=December 13, 2011|title=Arne Sorenson To Succeed Marriott Jr. As Marriott International CEO|publisher=[[RTTNews|RTTNews]]|url=http://www.rttnews.com/1780745/arne-sorenson-to-succeed-marriott-jr-as-marriott-international-ceo.aspx|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111214071521/http://www.rttnews.com/1780745/arne-sorenson-to-succeed-marriott-jr-as-marriott-international-ceo.aspx|archive-date=December 14, 2011}}</ref><ref name=":2" />其中[[万豪国际|万豪国际]]是其重要客户之一，1996年跳槽加入[[万豪国际|万豪国际]]担任顾问。<ref name=":2" />之后升迁为业务拓展副总裁。在位期间，经手对[[万丽酒店|万丽酒店]]出价100万美元的收购。<ref name=":3">{{Cite news|title=Arne Sorenson, CEO who grew Marriott into world’s largest hotel chain, dies at 62|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/local/obituaries/arne-sorenson-dead/2021/02/16/0875fa4e-7068-11eb-93be-c10813e358a2_story.html|url-status=live|work=[[The_Washington_Post|The Washington Post]]|last = Smith|first = Harrison|date = February 16, 2021}}</ref>在担任[[首席财务官|首席财务官]]和[[首席运营官|首席运营官]]后，2012年升迁为[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{cite web|title=Arne Morris Sorenson|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/profiles/people/2065017-arne-m-sorenson|url-status=dead|access-date=November 12, 2016|website = [[Bloomberg_News|Bloomberg News]]}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|last=Jr|first=J. W. "Bill" Marriott|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AxYA7Jo5T3kC&q=March+31%2C+2012%2C+arne+Sorenson+became+the+President+and+CEO+of+Marriott+International+Inc&pg=PT220|title=Without Reservations: How a Family Root Beer Stand Grew Into a Global Hotel Company|date=January 8, 2013|publisher=Diversion Books|isbn=978-1-938120-74-9|language=en}}</ref>也是除万豪家族以外首位执掌这家酒店集团的[[首席执行官|首席执行官]]。<ref>{{cite web|title=Archived copy|url=http://bethesda.patch.com/articles/marriott-ceo-passes-torch-of-bethesda-based-headquarters|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321212401/http://bethesda.patch.com/articles/marriott-ceo-passes-torch-of-bethesda-based-headquarters|archive-date=March 21, 2012|access-date=March 28, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Marriott CEO Arne Sorenson to have cancer surgery|url=https://www.bizjournals.com/washington/news/2019/11/07/marriott-ceo-arne-sorenson-to-have-cancer-surgery.html|access-date=April 29, 2020|website=www.bizjournals.com}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|date=October 29, 2014|title=Marriott News Center: Arne M. Sorenson|publisher=[[Marriott_International|Marriott International]]|url=http://news.marriott.com/arne-m-sorenson.html|url-status=dead|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120225022355/http://news.marriott.com/arne-m-sorenson.html|archive-date=February 25, 2012}}</ref>2016年以1300万美元收购[[喜达屋酒店及度假酒店国际集团|喜达屋酒店及度假酒店国际集团]]，将[[喜来登酒店|喜来登酒店]]，[[W飯店|W飯店]], [[威斯汀酒店|威斯汀酒店]]等品牌收入囊中。<ref name=":2" /><ref name=":3" /><ref>{{Cite news|last=Miller|first=Greg Roumeliotis, Matthew|date=April 1, 2016|title=China's Anbang abandons $14 billion bid to buy Starwood Hotels|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-starwood-hotels-m-a-anbang-idUSKCN0WX2PE|access-date=February 17, 2021}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Karmin|first=Craig|date=April 29, 2019|title=Marriott to Take On Airbnb in Booming Home-Rental Market|language=en-US|work=Wall Street Journal|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/marriott-to-take-on-airbnb-in-booming-home-rental-market-11556535600|access-date=February 17, 2021|issn=0099-9660}}</ref><ref name=":3" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=COVID-19: Marriott International CEO Arne Sorenson|url=https://www.hotelnewsresource.com/video57695.html|url-status=live|access-date=February 17, 2021|website=www.hotelnewsresource.com}}</ref> 

此外还担任[[微软|微软]]、[[沃尔玛|沃尔玛]]董事会成员，[[国际特殊奥林匹克组织|国际特殊奥林匹克组织]]和[[布鲁金斯学会|布鲁金斯学会]]成员。<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=Wal-Mart Board of Directors Nominates Two New Members|url=https://corporate.walmart.com/newsroom/2008/04/22/wal-mart-board-of-directors-nominates-two-new-members|access-date=February 17, 2021|website=Corporate - US|language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|title=Arne Sorenson|work=[[Forbes|Forbes]]|url=https://www.forbes.com/profile/arne-sorenson/|access-date=January 18, 2015}}</ref>

